# ===========================================
# WanderHive Chatbot — Google Maps Setup
# ===========================================
# Copy this file to `.env` in project root and fill in your key.

# REQUIRED for Google live photos + area info in chatbot:
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_google_maps_api_key_here

# Optional — smarter AI text replies:
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your_openai_key
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# -------------------------------------------
# How to get GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY (free trial):
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Create project → APIs & Services → Enable:
#    - Places API
#    - Places API (New) [optional]
# 3. Credentials → Create API Key
# 4. Restrict key to Places API + your domain (production)
# 5. Paste key above, save .env, restart: npm run dev
# -------------------------------------------
